    <h1>How to Train for <em>Kilimanjaro.</em></h1>
    <p>You don't need to be an elite athlete. You do need a solid cardio base, multi-day endurance under a loaded pack, and strong legs for a long descent. Here is the honest plan, with no padding.</p>
